Class AggregateReadEvent

  • java.lang.Object

          • org.seedstack.business.api.domain.events.AggregateReadEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<BaseValueObject>, DomainObject, ValueObject, Event, Producible

    public class AggregateReadEvent
extends BaseAggregateEvent
    Event fired when a method of a subtype of Repository annotated by @Read is called. This event will contains the method called of the repository and its arguments.

    To enable this interception add the following line in a props file: 

     [org.seedstack.business.event]
 domain.watch=true
    Author:
    pierre.thirouin@ext.mpsa.com
